title: Tell Zubeidi
description: Tell in the Hamrin Basin with a Kassite settlement dating from the 13th century BCE to the first half of the 12th. The area was flooded by the creation of the Hamrin Dam in the late 1970s.

properties.description: Point based on Google Earth representing the approximate location of Tell Zubeidi after Boehmer 1985.
properties.title: Approximate imagery location of Tell Zubeidi
